msgid ""
"Samba uses the SMB (server message block) protocol that is based on the "
"<phrase role=\"productname\">NetBIOS</phrase> services. Microsoft released "
"the protocol so other software manufacturers could establish connections to "
"a Microsoft domain network. With Samba, the SMB protocol works on top of the "
"TCP/IP protocol, so the TCP/IP protocol must be installed on all clients."
msgstr ""

