#. Tag: screen
#: net_samba.xml:1205 net_samba.xml:1225
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"rpcclient $&gt; netshareenum\n"
"netname: windows_server_2012_share\n"
"remark:\n"
"path:   C:\\Shares\\windows_server_2012_share\n"
"password:       (null)"
